          <div id="review_1047222_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  细说系列,其实不全是黎东方的作品,有后来别人为他整理填充的部分,那几本自然也就差了一些,另一些虽然也不错,但其它书籍中基本上写得齐全,没有更多个人的新意.而&lt;细说三国&gt;不论是内容还是文字,都活泼而自然,且写得恳切周全,从各方面来说都很值得一读.

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1047222/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1047222_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1047222_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8514676">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8514676/" class="title-link">读过第一部没有演绎成分的三国，后来才去看的三国志</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8514676"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/57970344/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u57970344-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/57970344/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">范筱宇</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-05-02"
      class="main-meta">2017-05-02 17:49:14</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8514676_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读过第一部没有演绎成分的三国，真实让当时的我眼界大开，看了10年书皮都翻烂了。相对当时市面上充斥的各种无学术根据的白文，要严谨的多，后来才有了易中天的电视节目，那时的易中天已经没有那么惊艳了。目录排版根据陈寿的三国志，列传形式，后面有三家的事，写得很详细，以...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8514676_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8514676_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










